#: src-en/data/events_sector_gathering.xml.append:6
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_gathering.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"DISTRESS_ORCHID_COLONY_FIRE\"]/mod-"
"append:choice/text"
msgstr "（霜晶壁垒）让霜晶壁垒用它的冰冻能力来扑灭火焰。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_gathering.xml.append:12
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_gathering.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_ORCHID_COLONY_FIRE_DEATHBLOOM\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"尽管身为水晶生物，霜晶壁垒仍热切相助，迅速行动起来。他在整个殖民地上空召唤了"
"一场暴风雪，数秒之内便将大火压制，救下了困在里面的每一株兰花。\n"
"……\n"
"……兰花们感激不尽。他们向你赠以大量礼物，并发誓将你们的善行传遍整个多元宇宙。"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_gathering.xml.append:17
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_gathering.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_DISTRESS_ORCHID_COLONY_FIRE_DEATHBLOOM\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"
